    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "I make my way to my room"
            ],
            [
                "The weight of the world is crawling in my back"
            ],
            [
                "I want to distract myself and do anything to avoid thinking what happened today."
            ],
            [
                "Why.. why is it that I can't be loved? My vision blurs, and I can feel my body shiver."
            ],
            [
                "I begin to crawl down the hole of solitude"
            ],
            [
                "A knock comes from the door"
            ],
            [
                "I open it"
            ],
            [
                "Hey, are you alright?"
            ],
            [
                "Helpie comes in and in stay in the bed."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, I've seen you down, what is going?"
            ],
            [
                "What happened?"
            ],
            [
                "Helpie... do you think..."
            ],
            [
                "Some people are unlovable?"
            ],
            [
                "Analizing....."
            ],
            [
                "I think some people don't know love."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie brings a blanket"
            ],
            [
                "As if some people don't understand the warmth or closeness they could give."
            ],
            [
                "Like this blanket"
            ],
            [
                "Helpie covers you with the blanket"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, but maybe... something is wrong. maybe... some of us don't deserve it."
            ],
            [
                "Something inherently flawed in us."
            ],
            [
                "Nah, bollocks."
            ],
            [
                "It's like coffee, everyone has their favourite coffee. But not everyone knows it."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie brings a coffee cup"
            ],
            [
                "Some don't even drink coffee, but that is because they haven't found their coffee"
            ],
            [
                "What if I'm more of a hot chocolate type."
            ],
            [
                "Well then, you would be glad to have someone know that detail about you."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie points to the cup and dispels a hot chocolate into the cup."
            ],
            [
                "But, how would you know?"
            ],
            [
                "Through time dear."
            ],
            [
                "Time to spend with someone."
            ],
            [
                "Days, months, years."
            ],
            [
                "Some enough to know well the depth of someone."
            ],
            [
                "To care, but to also know where and when to move and stop."
            ],
            [
                "Like knowing things about them?"
            ],
            [
                "No."
            ],
            [
                "Knowing things about you."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie screen shifted into a catalogue of movie selection screen."
            ],
            [
                "Like a movie you know will confort you."
            ]
        ],
